OL,3,CCocaine driver facing lengthy jail
OL,4,Cterm after 'careering' into teen at
OL,5,Cbus stop
OL,7,FA dangerous driver is facing a lengthy
OL,8,Fjail term after he admitted causing
OL,9,Fthe death of a teenager at a bus-stop
OL,10,Fwhile five times the drug drive limit.
OL,12,FSteven Wallace had been snorting
OL,13,Fcocaine the night before he lost
OL,14,Fcontrol of his BMW 320i in West
OL,15,FDenton, Newcastle, killing 19-year-old
OL,16,FJoe Scott and seriously injuring his
OL,17,Fgirlfriend.
