OL,3,CCocaine driver facing lengthy jail
OL,4,Cterm after 'careering' into teen at
OL,5,Cbus stop
OL,7,FThe 22-year-old pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fcausing death and serious injury by
OL,9,Fdangerous driving when he appeared at
OL,10,FNewcastle Crown Court on Monday 15
OL,11,FJuly.
OL,13,FWallace, of Millfield Close, in
OL,14,FNewburn, Newcastle, also admitted drug
OL,15,Fdriving, failing to stop after an
OL,16,Faccident and driving without insurance.
OL,18,FHe was remanded in custody and told he
OL,19,Ffaces a "substantial" spell behind
OL,20,Fbars when he is sentenced later this
OL,21,Fyear.
