OL,3,CCocaine driver facing lengthy jail
OL,4,Cterm after 'careering' into teen at
OL,5,Cbus stop
OL,7,FJudge Christopher Prince told him:
OL,8,F"You know you are going to receive a
OL,9,Fsubstantial custodial sentence for
OL,10,Fthis horrific bit of driving,
OL,11,Fcareering off the road on a Sunday
OL,12,Fafternoon.
OL,14,F"You are going to stay in custody
OL,15,Funtil you are sentenced.
OL,17,F"You were over five times over the
OL,18,Fcocaine limit, taken the night before
OL,19,Fbroken down in your system. I've no
OL,20,Fidea why you used so much cocaine.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
