OL,3,CCocaine driver facing lengthy jail
OL,4,Cterm after 'careering' into teen at
OL,5,Cbus stop
OL,7,F"I'm certainly not going to submit the
OL,8,Fpublic to the risk of you using
OL,9,Fcocaine or driving dangerously again.
OL,10,FAccordingly you will remain in
OL,11,Fcustody."
OL,13,FJoe, from Blakelaw, in Newcastle, died
OL,14,Fat the scene after he was struck by
OL,15,FWallace's car as he waited for a bus
OL,16,Fon West Denton Way, in West Denton,
OL,17,FNewcastle, at around 4pm on Sunday 15
OL,18,FOctober.
