OL,5,Cbus stop
OL,7,FRichard Herrmann, mitigating, said
OL,8,FWallace, who was around five times the
OL,9,Flimit for cocaine breakdown product
OL,10,FBenzolecgonine, has no previous
OL,11,Fconvictions and had a clean driving
OL,12,Flicence.
OL,14,FHe added that his client has two young
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,FWallace will be sentenced at Newcastle
OL,18,FCrown Court on 11 October.
